ps://apps.qoo-app.com/app/9558#COMMENT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F9558%23COMMENT&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbsQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=5f34a72c\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/9558#COMMENT</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WPJtOcYYpbQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWPJtOcYYpbQ&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbsQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=be8837b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WPJtOcYYpbQ</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MQio0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MQio0v.jpg&h=71635929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OLb9vFu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOLb9vFu.jpg&h=40854827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XakPoHd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXakPoHd.jpg&h=a2f02729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BVeGNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BVeGNc.jpg&h=994f57d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《三國志 Heroes 英雄》</strong>是一款三國志題材的棋盤式回合制戰鬥遊戲，在遊戲中再現了三國時代的英傑們馳騁沙場的英姿。本作同時擁有桌上遊戲簡單易上手的特性和電子競技的競技性，採用將棋、圍棋等棋類遊戲玩法，在輕鬆簡單的規則下，玩家在策略上的佈置將是取得勝利的關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n#三國志Heroz #三国志ヒーローズ<br />\n開服日子：2月3日。<br />\n遊戲玩法係調配8-12個武將（按上陣cost）每個武將有唔同能力，攻擊及移動方式，之後雙方 battle。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>首抽</strong>：入Game完成教學，第一次首抽個個一樣，5星孫策（騎兵）及指定既3-4星將。<br />\n第一日登入送5星劉備（騎兵）。<br />\n之後再自己會有 1券+1000石。拎曬去抽張飛活動包。抽唔中5星就del game data重開始。<br />\n或者睇埋初級教學場說明+打多3,4關卡，儲夠2100石可以8連抽。（保証一隻4星+）。<br />\n<br />\n日文 簡易武將評價：<br />\n<a href=\"https://game8.jp/sangokushi-heroes/314314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame8.jp%2Fsangokushi-heroes%2F314314&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbsQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=e0a24e77\" target=\"_blank\">https://game8.jp/sangokushi-heroes/314314</a><br />\n<br />\n登入滿7日/或者課HK$40/打pvp會有5星交換券，可換各國一指定5星將：（有許諸, 黃忠，孫權等）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">PVP Fever時間</span></strong> 香港 11am, 8pm一個鐘，無限箱打。推薦必打。閒時可付$30石打箱。開箱會升 活動pt分,同特定箱（&ldquo;登用門&rdquo;）會開武將。<br />\n<br />\n打故事Mode有機會出箱（畫面開始有跌箱先有）可能有武將。<br />\n希望大家人人抽中趙雲。<br />\n不過首抽建議武將：<br />\n蜀國：張飛》馬超》趙雲<br />\n他國：呂玲綺<br />\n魏國：司馬懿"},{"pid":"318299ff0092667ae2b4e5bd56d45274f27d2718","tid":1964798,"uid":315833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"你班衰仔個個懶開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到1000 就寧願唔出聲都唔肯中1001 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是但開個頂住先"},{"pid":"5aadeea8f3be95a06191291898df139fea68b7c6","tid":1964798,"uid":355386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:13:55.000Z","msg":"首8抽無最强最屈機的張飛就應del,  否則好難抽得番（因為張飛已復刻左1次）， 其他5星都有接近代替品"},{"pid":"e02ac9889984d02ae74adca647d8dee798bff690","tid":1964798,"uid":315833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aadeea8f3be95a06191291898df139fea68b7c6","tid":1964798,"uid":355386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:13:55.000Z","msg":"首8抽無最强最屈機的張飛就應del,  否則好難抽得番（因為張飛已復刻左1次）， 其他5星都有接近代替品"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T08:29:25.000Z","msg":"張飛強在起手三個方向"},{"pid":"41b4a8de2eb7ef507e90664b613a0d0237f9d737","tid":1964798,"uid":315833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"Btw 有新post了<br />\n用翻呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[A/I] 三國志 Heroes 戰棋類遊戲 火熱登場，越來越多人玩 (3)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1964306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1964306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f874cacf0db8650a4a0d8aa8d